 With homogeneous risk perceptions, both types would set 
\begin_inset Formula $c_{t}$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $u'=\bar{\tilde{\mu}}_{t}$
\end_inset

, giving homogeneous consumption denoted 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{c}_{t}$
\end_inset

.
