 (-1 for NYT; -2/3 for MSNBC; -1/3 for CNN; 0 for Network; 1/3 for WSJ;
 2/3 for Fox News; 1 for Breitbart).
 The weighted average of news partisanship for each participant equals the
 sum of (Answer * Source Partisanship) divided by the sum of Answer.
 
